>>LISA: It is.

00:42:50.633 --> 00:42:53.920 align:middle line:84%
It's that creative
power, essentially.

00:42:53.920 --> 00:42:54.890 align:middle line:90%
>>ORLOFF: Yes, exactly.

00:42:54.890 --> 00:42:57.130 align:middle line:84%
And there's a meditation
I have in the book.

00:42:57.130 --> 00:42:59.110 align:middle line:84%
