00:43:54.470 --> 00:43:57.690 align:middle line:84%
The endorphins start flowing
in your brain and your body,

00:43:57.690 --> 00:43:59.039 align:middle line:90%
making you feel good.

00:43:59.039 --> 00:44:00.830 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that's an
example of surrender.

